            "title": "盤中速報 - 華納兄弟探索(WBD-US)大漲5.02%，報11.71美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華納兄弟探索(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WBD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WBD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WBD-US</a>)截至台北時間27日23:08股價上漲0.56美元，報11.71美元，漲幅5.02%，成交量24,168,126（股），盤中最高價11.71美元、最低價11.18美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.92%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.59%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.5%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.57%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>華納兄弟探索(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WBD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WBD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WBD-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+5.49%</li> <li>近 1 月：+23.89%</li> <li>近 3 月：+1.09%</li> <li>近 6 月：+4.99%</li> <li>今年以來：+5.49%</li></ul></section></main>",
